        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1989",
        "content": "\"She would look strange among the vines and the roses now.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1989_26962_000007_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1989/26962/1989_26962_000007_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1989",
        "content": "\"For Dino's sake,\" she said to herself.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1989_26962_000007_000007",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1989/26962/1989_26962_000007_000007.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1989",
        "content": "The first said-",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1989_26962_000008_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1989/26962/1989_26962_000008_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1989",
        "content": "\"Tito, my love for you is dead; and therefore, so far as I was yours, I too am dead.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1989_26962_000008_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1989/26962/1989_26962_000008_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1989",
        "content": "Do not try to put in force any laws for the sake of fetching me back: that would bring you no happiness.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1989_26962_000008_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1989/26962/1989_26962_000008_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1989",
        "content": "The Romola you married can never return.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1989_26962_000008_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1989/26962/1989_26962_000008_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1989",
        "content": "I need explain nothing to you after the words I uttered to you the last time we spoke long together.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1989_26962_000009_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1989/26962/1989_26962_000009_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1989",
        "content": "\"I think you will fulfil my wish that my bridal chest should be sent to my godfather, who gave it me.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1989_26962_000009_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1989/26962/1989_26962_000009_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1989",
        "content": "It contains my wedding clothes and the portraits and other relics of my father and mother.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1989_26962_000011_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1989/26962/1989_26962_000011_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1989",
        "content": "But now I am gone. Do not ask the reason; and if you love my father, try to prevent any one from seeking me.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1989_26962_000011_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1989/26962/1989_26962_000011_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1989",
        "content": "I could not bear my life at Florence.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1989_26962_000011_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1989/26962/1989_26962_000011_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1989",
        "content": "I cannot bear to tell any one why.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1989_26962_000011_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1989/26962/1989_26962_000011_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1989",
        "content": "Help to cover my lot in silence.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1989_26962_000011_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1989/26962/1989_26962_000011_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1989",
        "content": "I have asked that my bridal chest should be sent to you: when you open it, you will know the reason.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1989_26962_000011_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1989/26962/1989_26962_000011_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1989",
        "content": "Please to give all the things that were my mother's to my cousin Brigida, and ask her to forgive me for not saying any words of parting to her.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1989_26962_000012_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1989/26962/1989_26962_000012_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1989",
        "content": "\"Farewell, my second father.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1989_26962_000012_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1989/26962/1989_26962_000012_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1989",
        "content": "The best thing I have in life is still to remember your goodness and be grateful to you.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1989_26962_000013_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1989/26962/1989_26962_000013_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1989",
        "content": "\"Romola.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-1989_26962_000014_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/1989/26962/1989_26962_000014_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-1989",
        "content": "She was ready now to depart.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
